Game information:

Octodad: Dadliest Catch - is a game about destruction,
cunning, and fatherhood. The player will control Osmipapoy,
agile octopus masquerading man. Osmipapy life passes in a
constant struggle in which he had to cope with everyday
tasks with your boneless tentacles while keeping its essence
osminozhyu secret from his human family.

In this sequel to the original adventure Osmipapy Headfoot
our hero finds himself in another wrangle - with growing
distrust of his wife, he is forced to take only an unsuccessful
campaign in the local aquarium. If you have enough of his father's
qualities to control octopus titled father while he tries to
hide its marine origin from the family and leave their tentacles unharmed?

In October 2010, a team of students in the world has released the
original version of Octodad. Despite the general belief that it is
just an ordinary human father simulator, the game became a cult hit,
received press coverage and was a finalist in the student category "
Independent Games Festival" 2011 (Independent Games Festival).
Octodad attracted enough attention to coerce team on a fundraising
campaign on Kickstarter and the formation of the studio Young
Horses - all in order to make a new game about Osmipapu bigger,
better and give proper polishing. After two and a half years
after the start of development, Octodad: Dadliest Catch
(in pereveode "Osmipapa: Paternal Catch")
is ready to flop awkwardly in your arms.
